         <ab>VrS78.12 (mss. 2005, 2007, 2010, 2030, 2040, 2101, 2104, 2106, 2109, 4010, 4020, 4025, 4040, 4050, 4055, 4060, 4161, 4162, 5020):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ēsm ud bōy sē tāg frāz nihādan zōt ud rāspīg <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> sē guftan</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "He (the <em>rāspīg</em>) should put three pieces of <em>ēsm</em> and <em>bōy</em> into the fire. The <em>zōt</em> and the <em>rāspīg</em> should recite three 
            <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em>."</ab>
